About us

An application that allows expecting/current parents and professional counselors to come together. It helps you connect with other expecting/current parents through a chat/forum, has addition resources for parent dealing with stress, postpartum depression, and other related issues that come with having a family. It also provides users with therapists to work with for effectively dealing with postpartum issues. Group 1

    Raymond Johnson, Blanca Monir Hossen and Phillip Mitchell
